# Mithril Whisper Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and configure for your setup

# === LOCAL DEVELOPMENT MODE ===
# For GitHub users who want to run locally with their own OpenAI key
# Only OPENAI_API_KEY is required for full functionality
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# === PRODUCTION/PROPRIETARY MODE ===  
# For the official DMG installer (uses proprietary Supabase backend)
# Uncomment these lines for production deployment
# SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key

# === MODES EXPLAINED ===
# 1. LOCAL MODE: Only OPENAI_API_KEY set
#    - Assistant calls OpenAI API directly
#    - No authentication required
#    - Perfect for development/testing
#
# 2. PRODUCTION MODE: SUPABASE_URL + SUPABASE_ANON_KEY set
#    - Uses proprietary Supabase Edge Functions
#    - Requires user authentication  
#    - Used in official DMG installer
#
# 3. TRANSCRIPTION ONLY: No API keys set
#    - Basic transcription works (Whisper.cpp only)
#    - Assistant features disabled
